| Library | Version | Notes |
|---------|---------|-------|
| leaflet | 1.9.4 | `npm install leaflet@1.9.4` |
| react | 18.3.1 | Pin to 18, not 19 |
| react-dom | 18.3.1 | same |
| vite | latest | `@vitejs/plugin-react` |

**CartoDB Voyager tiles:**
```
URL: https://{s}.basemaps.cartocdn.com/rastertiles/voyager/{z}/{x}/{y}{r}.png
Attribution: &copy; <a href="https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright">OpenStreetMap</a> contributors &copy; <a href="https://carto.com/attributions">CARTO</a>
maxZoom: 19
```

**Google Fonts (load in index.html `<head>`):**
```html
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
```

**API base:** `https://api.michaelwegter.com` (all `/mn-parks/*` routes)
**Demo account:** `demo@mnparks.test` / `Parks2024!`
**JWT key:** `mn_parks_token` in localStorage
**JWT header:** `Authorization: Bearer <token>`

