- decisions: ArcGIS endpoint confirmed 404; Wikipedia lat/lng data is the sole coordinate source and is confirmed complete for all 73 parks; use vanilla Leaflet (not react-leaflet) with useRef/useEffect; React 18 not 19; vite outDir points directly to michaelwegter.com/public/demos/
- next needs: demo-builder pastes parks.js directly; use scaffold command verbatim; DO NOT use react-leaflet; mount Leaflet map in useEffect; add photo DELETE route per CEO directive; cover letter must state Google Maps production path
